Edition:
Quote: Your Donkey Has Eaten My Passport. [woman telling story of another woman being asked to wear a furcoat through customs to get someone out of paying duty] `The original person who was trying to work the slinter couldn't do anything about it.'
Notes: 1982 February 14 10.20.a.m. 2YA

